init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is not aware that Matt Damon is a very important person to the human race.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is also a master of disguise and can be anyone he wants to be.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is unaware that the human race will stop at nothing to retrieve Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are called the "Matt Damon Retrieval Team" and they are the most elite group of humans on the planet.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is not aware of this, but he is about to get a rude awakening.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Swiss team is not going to let the alien have his way with Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are going to get Matt Damon back, no matter what.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are going to get Matt Damon back, even if they have to destroy Planet Borg in the process.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien had been very cruel to Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is not happy that he has been defeated by the Swiss.
